Importing JSON:
    JavaScript Object Notation
    Data interchange format 

eg:

{
    "name":"Bruce Wayne",
    "addresss": {
        "street": "Wayne Manor",
        "city" : "Gotham" 
    }
}

Access it by:

const data = require("./data.json") //or remove .json
console.log(data);

